data.description: Beautiful Century Community home located in a gated community. This home features a well-appointed open kitchen with plenty of cabinet space and stainless steel appliances. Downstairs has an open layout as well as a den with sliding barn door and plenty of natural lighting. Upstairs you'll find a large loft and laundry room with extra storage. Primary bedroom is spacious and offers a large walk-in closet, dual sinks and separate tub and shower. Don't miss out on this home, come see it today!
